Package sketch.compiler

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Directive
    An odd little class for interpreting compiler directives, such as #pragma options "--heapsize 10 --reorderEncoding exponential" This class is responsible for recognizing and storing the directives.
    Directive.InstrumentationDirective
    instrument reads and writes of an array in cuda functions
    Directive.OptionsDirective
    A pragma to set within a source file the SKETCH options normally passed through the command line.
